Multiple variables
========================================================
type: section

There are at least six elements of a plot that can be assigned to variables:

* x-axis
* y-axis
* facets
* color/fill
* size
* shape (e.g., dots vs crosses, solid vs dashed lines, etc.)

Two categorical variables
